I've had my Arro for 14 years. Yes you read that right.
The main zipper is starting to have issues, but otherwise it has performed flawlessly all over the world.
It's a bit lacking interior pockets/organizers, but otherwise I wouldn't hesitate recommending it very highly.
Being so old it's made in Canada, but hopefully the new ones are equally good.

Cons: lacks inner pockets
